Has anyone else had a real hard time targetting since SOE made Directx 9 a *must*.
<br />

<br />
I swear I've done well over 20 hard adv since the patch and at one point it was d*mn near impossible to target any mob in another room than you.  Since the last patch its been better, but nowhere near where it was before the whole directx9 patch.   Sro adv has got to be the worst for targetting.  I'll pull, get an add run backwards to my group wildly clicking the screen to target the add and never could.  Then to add insult to injury even when he was on top of me I couldn't target him, I had to ESC my target and let myself get hit to target him.  UGH!<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-12.gif" border="0" alt="Mad" hspace="2" />
